title: 🧨1 Bed 1 Bath with Massive Square Footage 🧨
posting_body: ['🤗', 'Nice location in Southwest Austin, this spot gives you privacy while only being a 15 minute drive to downtown.', 'Get to Dripping Springs for a day trip easily.', 'Brand new grocery store next door, 3 minutes to beautiful nature park.', '🌟 Apartment boasts large square footage, clean light contemporary feel with white quartz countertops, white subway tile backsplashes, clean white cabinetry with TONS of storage.', '🏎️ Want a private garage for more storage or for your nice car?', 'Rent one!', '🏊\u200d♀️ Gorgeous sparkling pool with grilling stations.', '🏋️\u200d♂️ Clean gym with state of the art equipment.', 'Taylor Boykin', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Craft Apartment Locators', 'My service is 100% FREE for you!', "Text for more info or a tour and we'll get you set!", 'Moving from out of town?', 'No problem, let me know', 'and I can get videos of the units/property myself to be sent over to you.', "🙌 Is this close to what you're looking for, but not quite it?", 'Shoot me a message and we can get going on a search that matches your needs!', "I'm here to get you a great deal at great properties.", '🙌', '*Pricing and lease terms subject to change by the property.', 'Pictures are taken from the property but may not be exact unit.', 'No worries!', 'I can get you all the detailed info over to you.*', '😃Serving all Austin areas: North Austin / South Austin / Central Austin / East Austin | SoLa | South Congress | Lady Bird Lake | Downtown | Travis Heights | Central | Barton | Lamar | Clarksville | Crestview | Zilker | Domain | SoCo | South Central | Oak Hill | Bee Cave | Lake Travis | Southpark Meadows | Arboretum | 78704 | 78703 | 78702 | 78701 | 78745']
